Following are notes from the original 2015 project:
---
Most of the early notes are summarized on the wikipage:
 http://cm-7-w.lanl.gov/lore/SlurmFS working notes

---
Although this is written as "SlurmFS" this is with the conscious intention
that a revision into production code would factor this out into a "rmfs"
(resource manager file system) layer and a modularized RM implementation layer
via a resource manager switch function. One implementation of the interface would
be slurm as the resource manager. Others would follow.
---

